content.visibleText:
name: Deploy

on:
  push:
    branches:
      - master
    paths:
      - 'configs/**'
      - 'packages.json'

jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Setup Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v2
        with:
          node-version: '14'
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: |
          npm config set //npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken ${{ secrets.TRIL...
